  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When user tries to change a transaction fee and she taps near the slider the whole specify amount popup hides. This can be really frustrating.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nSpecify amount popup does not hide when tapped.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nWhen you tap inside red rectangles shown on the following picture, the popup hides:\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/37719898-6eeee3fe-2d26-11e8-95de-3158db7c0d25.png\" width=\"300\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open 1-1 chat\r\n- Type \"/send 0.001\" and wait for the specify amount popup\r\n- Tap somewhere on the popup\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, March 21\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
